oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry star Roger Miller at Jo Vonn Inn
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Miller, Roger, 1936-1992; Pierce, Webb, 1921-1991; Wood, Del; Carlisle, Bill;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry stars Roger Miller, Webb Pierce, Del Wood, Bill Carlisle and the Carlisles at the Joe Vonn Inn on August 12. Poster features metal photoplates of Roger Miller, Webb Pierce, Del Wood, and Bill Carlisle.
